git sync [<options>] - Synchronize changes and update submodules

    -h|--help               display help
    -q|--quiet              don't print submodule name when synchronizing
    -0|--level0             do not synchronize submodules (only working directory)
    -s|--sm-only            synchronize submodules only (skip working directory)
    -e|--stop-on-error      stop looping as soon as command fails (exit code != 0)
    
example:
    git sync                # synchronize working dir and submodules recursively
    git sync -0             # synchronize working dir only and update submodules
    git sync -s             # synchronize submodules recursively (skip working directory)